IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User YOUR@gmail.com
PassCmd "cat /path/to/apppassword.txt"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path /data/maildir/
Inbox /data/maildir/INBOX
AltMap yes      # required: embeds IMAP UID as a numeric prefix in filenames
                # filename format: {uid}_{timestamp}.{pid}.{host}:2,flags

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:\All
Near :gmail-local:"All Mail"
Create Near
Sync Pull       # one-directional: remote → local only, never the reverse
Expunge Near    # remove local copies when they disappear from Gmail (after Trash)
SyncState *

# Usage:
#   mbsync -a              # full / incremental sync
#   mbsync gmail           # this channel only
#
# Cron example (daily at 3 AM):
#   0 3 * * * mbsync -a && docker compose -f /path/to/docker-compose.yml run --rm app fetch
